Author: anfroholic
Content:
Just assembled the first test COB. 
I think I pretty much like the form factor. 
With 70pins they hold on there pretty good. 

Some conversations with other people, they had mentioned mezzanine connectors to the a weak point, but these seem pretty solid. 

I think I'm pretty happy with them overall.
